data.description: Freshly painted inside! This charming 3 bed 2 bath brick home will be an adorable starter home for a growing family. The open concept kitchen is spacious and great for anyone who loves to cook. The living room is inviting with a cozy wood burning fireplace. Both bathrooms have been updated and offer an attractive retreat. The spacious backyard is perfect for entertaining. There's a nice sized multipurpose building in the backyard, with electricity, that can be used for a workshop, additional living quarters, or storage.
